RewriteEngine On

# Force HTTPS
RewriteCond %{HTTPS} off
RewriteRule ^(.*)$ https://%{HTTP_HOST}%{REQUEST_URI} [L,R=301]

# Force www
RewriteCond %{HTTP_HOST} !^www\. [NC]
RewriteRule ^(.*)$ https://www.%{HTTP_HOST}%{REQUEST_URI} [L,R=301]

# Remove multiple slashes
RewriteCond %{THE_REQUEST} //
RewriteRule ^.*$ $0 [R=301,L,NE]
```

---

## Nach dem Deployment

Teste diese URLs – alle sollten auf **eine** canonical URL redirecten:
```
http://trailmq.com/                      → https://www.trailmq.com/
http://www.trailmq.com/                  → https://www.trailmq.com/
https://trailmq.com/                     → https://www.trailmq.com/
https://www.trailmq.com/                 ← ✅ FINAL

http://trailmq.com/architecture-thinking → https://www.trailmq.com/architecture-thinking/
https://www.trailmq.com/architecture-thinking/ ← ✅ FINAL